videos.description: Lamar Peters passes it in between two defenders for Reggie Perry to grab it and throw it down.
videos.headline: Perry snags it between 2 defenders for the dunk

videos.description: Lamar Peters hits his 8th 3-pointer of the game to get to 26 points, setting his career high to put Mississippi State up 84-69.
videos.headline: Peters sets career-high with 26th point
